  --no-build              Skip auto-build after agent completes (deck.md only)
                          仅生成 deck.md，不自动渲染
  --force                 Skip confirmation prompt (delete subcommand)
                          跳过确认提示（delete 子命令）
  --help, -h              Show this help
                          显示本帮助
",
}
